                            <comment id="14084184" author="aholmber" created="Mon, 4 Aug 2014 00:41:59 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Yes. Tested patch with similar results on 2.1 (java 7), 2.0 (java 7), 1.2 (java 6,7)&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14084588" author="jbellis" created="Mon, 4 Aug 2014 12:21:09 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Can you have a look, &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=snazy&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;snazy&quot;&gt;snazy&lt;/a&gt;?&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14084685" author="snazy" created="Mon, 4 Aug 2014 14:09:18 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Yep. But currently -1 on the patch (since it&apos;s now IPv6 only - but illustrated the cause).&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14084719" author="snazy" created="Mon, 4 Aug 2014 14:48:20 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Sorry for the &quot;-1&quot; - have to revert it to a &quot;+1&quot;!&lt;br/&gt;
Patch LGTM&lt;/p&gt;

